metadata.name: 015 Golden Fossil Orchid
metadata.description:
#015 of our limited 100 NFTs plant collection. The Golden Fossil Orchid stands out with its rare metallic golden texture and poetic posture, constantly whispering out of your past, present and future victories. 

We warmly welcome you to come and following the footsteps of our digital botanist, continue to explore the great unknown in the virtual eden of the MetaOasis.
